sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant Proxy as integrated_proxy.py
    participant MW as HTTP Middleware
    participant LiteLLM as LiteLLM Router
    participant Anthropic as Anthropic API
    participant Azure as Azure OpenAI
    participant Cache as Response Cache

    Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/messages
    Proxy->>MW: log request, start timer
    MW->>LiteLLM: route to provider

    alt Primary provider (Anthropic)
        LiteLLM->>Anthropic: forward request
        Anthropic-->>LiteLLM: streaming response
    else Fallback (Azure OpenAI)
        LiteLLM->>Azure: forward request
        Azure-->>LiteLLM: streaming response
    end

    LiteLLM-->>Proxy: SSE chunks
    Proxy->>Cache: cache if eligible
    Proxy-->>Client: stream SSE response
    MW->>MW: log response time, metrics
